      You have successfully sent a holiday information email to waldendairy.com,
      your dates are from: <%= @customer_holiday.try(:from_date) %> to date: <%= @customer_holiday.try(:to_date) %>.<br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      Here are the instructions you have given us:
      <%= @customer_holiday.try(:notes) %> <br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      To login to the site, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thank you for your custom.</p>
    <p></p><%= link_to "Follow us on twitter", "http://twitter.com/waldendairy", :target => "_blank"  %>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <p></p>
    <p>
     <%= link_to (image_tag attachments['small_sh_banner.png'].url), "http://saffronhosts.com", :target => "_blank"  %>
    </p>
